{"build_type":"executable","description":"LLM reader op.xref (reverse edges) with envelope. Request (argv[1]): {\"xref\":{\"symbol\":\"<name>\",\"roots\":[\"<dir>\",...]}}. SELF-BUILDS the dependency graph in RAM from roots via collect_dependency_graph_from_roots (no graph passed in), then cross-references the symbol. Emits {symbol, defined_in, callers, granularity, confidence, omitted}: defined_in=packages that define the symbol, callers=packages whose call list mentions it (the reverse edge op.read cannot give). granularity=package (answers which PACKAGE, not which function). confidence=exact-symbol-match if defined or called anywhere, else not-found. omitted.packages_scanned=corpus size. Bad request (no argv, unparseable, no arg object, no symbol or roots field) -> clean JSON {error}, no crash. Reuses parse_argument_vector_json_request, locate_named_member_inside_mapping, collect_dependency_graph_from_roots, collect_graph_packages_whose_field_lists_symbol, add_str_field, json-tree-node, finalize_reader_response_envelope.","module_name":"cross-reference-symbol-across-dependency-graph","package_name":"cross-reference-symbol-across-dependency-graph","function_definitions":{"cross-reference-symbol-across-dependency-graph":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"__argc","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"__argv","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_roots","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"roots"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_calls","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"calls"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_defines","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"define